message.content: OpenAI is an artificial intelligence research laboratory and company. It was founded in December 2015 and focuses on developing AI technologies and promoting their safe and responsible use. OpenAI aims to ensure that artificial general intelligence (AGI), which refers to highly autonomous systems that can outperform humans at most economically valuable work, benefits all of humanity. The organization conducts cutting-edge research, releases most of its AI work as open-source projects, and collaborates with other institutions and companies to advance AI capabilities.
